title: Heroes of a Broken Land v1.8e
description:
Heroes of a Broken Land v1.8e


Extract 7zip & play!



Changes

    Can change party formation in the world and dungeons
    Fix issue where loading during battle left battle UI on screen
    Fix issue where loading from a monster dungeon could break the game
    Adjust Fae and Lizard recruit generation rate
    Always provide a Lv 1 Fae and Lizard in allied towns
